  "description": {
    "zh": "我受够了你搞的所有这些“恶作剧”——说得轻点。你对我来说很特别，一个我认为可以信任的人，我张开双臂欢迎你，而你和你的朋友做了什么？这就是你表示感谢的方式吗？好吧，你很幸运我没有让人一见到你就开枪，至少期待一些感激吧。\n\n这里有好消息，如果你甚至能称之为“好”的话。我这里有份长长的清单，全是没人想做的公开合同，你知道我想把所有有趣的工作都留给你，但你想这样，现在享受做所有脏活吧。你甚至还有工作就应该高兴了！在你对我的人做了所有那些事之后，我甚至很难直视你的眼睛，但我喜欢看到人们好的一面——然而，别把这当成我原谅你了，我绝对鄙视你所做的事，但我们也许能把这事抛在脑后……大部分地。\n\n让我们从一些不容易搞砸的事情开始，并且没有什么你可以利用的，你明白吗？这是清单，在完成之前我不想再听到你说一个字。",
    "en": "I am sick and tired of all these \"pranks\" you pulled - To put it lightly. You are someone special to me, someone I thought could be trusted, I welcomed you with open arms and what did you and your friends do? Is this your way of saying thanks? Alright then, you're lucky im not letting people shoot you on sight, let me at least expect some gratitude.\n\nHere are the good news, if you can even call it \"good\". I have a long list right here, full of open contracts that nobody wants to do, you know I wanted to reserve all the interesting jobs for you but you wanted it to be this way, now enjoy doing all the dirty work. You should be happy you even get work at all! After everything that you did to my people, I even have trouble looking into your eyes, but I like seeing the good in people - However, don't see this as me forgiving you, I absolutely despise what you did, but we might be able to leave this behind us... Mostly.\n\nLet's start with something that can't be messed up easily, and nothing which you can exploit, you understand that? Here's the list, I don't want to hear another word from you until this is completed."
  },
